Methods

Pulled live dataset directly from NYC Open Data API
Filtered for records where Is the data set on Open Data? == "Not on Open Data Plan"
Sorted denied datasets by FOIL request volume to identify highest-demand suppressions
Calculated overall denial rate as share of total tracked datasets
Derived denial reason taxonomy from agency public statements column

Data Source
NYC Open Data — Agency Open Data Plans and FOIL Requests
https://data.cityofnewyork.us/api/views/93kn-fhqt/rows.csv
